 ## Legacy compatibility
 - Legacy plaintext endpoint remains:
   - `GET /api/v2/questionnaires/history/{session_id}/results`
-- It is JWT-protected and returns:
-  - `X-CognIA-Endpoint-Status: legacy_plaintext`
